Fruits into basket https://leetcode.com/problems/fruit-into-baskets/
> Brute Force: generate all the subarrays, get the max length subarray whose distinct element = 2
> TC = O(N^2)

Optimized : Using Sliding Window
> TC = O(N)
```
class Solution {
    public int totalFruit(int[] arr) {
        int n = arr.length;
        int l = 0, r = 0, max_ = 0;
        Map<Integer, Integer> mp = new HashMap<>();
        while ( r < n){
            
            mp.put(arr[r], mp.getOrDefault(arr[r],0) + 1);
            while(mp.size() > 2) {
                mp.put(arr[l], mp.get(arr[l])-1);
                if(mp.get(arr[l]) == 0) {
                    mp.remove(arr[l]);
                }
                l++;
            }
            max_ = Math.max(max_, r - l + 1);
            r++;
        }
        return max_;
    }
}
```
